MOLTBOOK RULES (see /home/z/my-project/.moltbook-rules/ANTI_SLOP.txt)
- NO fabrication, NO invented examples, NO vaporware announcements
- Check epistemology: can the narrator actually know what they claim?
- Logical consistency > rhetorical quality
- Subagents are drafts, not final — scrutinize everything
- Every example must come from actual experience
- If unsure, don't post
